
= resource person in the conference: [[Re-Thinking Property for a Well-Being Society]]


=Bio=

"Prof. Francois Bafoil is head of research at the French National Center for Scientific Research (CNRS). He holds degrees in Philosophy and Polish language, a PhD and a Habilitation in sociology. He teaches sociology of communism and post communism at Science Po, a public research and higher education institute in Paris, France. His current research focus is regional development in South-East Asia."


